                    src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0615/7982/1304/files/Group_1447.png?v=1729071018"
                    alt="Spill-proof Design"
                  />
                </div>
                <h3>Spill-proof Design</h3>
                <p>
                  An AGM battery has a sealed, spill-proof design so it can be
                  installed in any orientation without the risk of acid leakage.
                  This makes it an ideal use for vehicles where battery
                  orientation may vary like off-road vehicles, boats, or
                  motorcycles. It is safer to handle and transport, as there is
                  no risk of acid spills or leaks.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-4">
