                    src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0615/7982/1304/files/Group_1450.png?v=1729071019"
                    alt="Fast Charging"
                  />
                </div>
                <h3>Fast Charging</h3>
                <p>
                  An AGM battery can handle charge rates of 30-50 amps, compared
                  to only 10 amps for regular batteries. You can charge it much
                  faster using a higher current without damaging it. Just be
                  sure to follow manufacturer recommendations and guidelines to
                  ensure safe and effective fast charging.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-4">
